{"tid":1434833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後所有女義士都唔可以落單！！自己一定要睇路！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:17:51.000Z","uid":200158,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a06dca7184d46bbf7d27a520442e61b0f9809327","tid":1434833,"uid":200158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"［推到女事主回應］女義士比數十狗壓在地上輪摸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434599</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一早見到呢個Po同睇完條片 我真係覺得勁心痛<br />\n大家都係女人我完全睇到勁憤慨<br />\n點可以會有幾十隻狗非禮一個落單既女仔<br />\n呢埸運動少咗邊個都唔得 佢地咁做係唔會嚇到我地<br />\n去到今時今日 我地已經唔可以退縮 冇得再返轉頭<br />\n但我真係唔想再見到有任何女生因爲啲目無法紀既警犬而蒙受陰影<br />\n由於女事主未出黎回應 冒住炒車既危險我都要講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以後所有女仔都唔可以落單！自己一個係條街快快趣走咗先啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家見到呢啲情況一定要救人 唔好掛住拍片應承我啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n題外話：究竟有冇女權撚可以組織翻一次遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e15a9ffcfb81688c7b1e4d72fbb86ccba00f8f","tid":1434833,"uid":200158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"86581485469be6afb4ff2f03291e69273f084033","tid":1434833,"uid":200158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到真係好嬲"},{"pid":"0aee8bf477844ae64453de18b0cb3401b0993c8a","tid":1434833,"uid":200158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"